  (4, 'screenwriting', 'D', 'Would benefit from from clearer dramatic tension. Advice to give each scene clear conflict, escalate the stakes, and control pacing so engagement holds — sustained tension comes through repeated practice and feedback.'),
  (4, 'screenwriting', 'D', 'Needs to practice and to explore applying non-linear structures. Advice to give each time-shift a clear story reason so that shifts in time and narrative remain purposeful and coherent— purposeful, coherent non-linear writing comes through repeated practice and feedback.'),
  (4, 'screenwriting', 'D', 'Needs to work on montage. Advice to plan a clear visual progression and decide how sound and rhythm carry the narrative intent — effective montage comes through repeated practice and feedback.'),
