  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Applies lenses and depth of field with awareness. Advice to develop stronger control by testing different apertures and focal lengths before the shoot, so depth choices reliably strengthen each image.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Uses composition and camera angles effectively in parts. Advice to make framing more consistent by setting clear compositional rules per scene — balance and headroom that hold across shots grow with regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Maintains basic continuity. Advice to improve visual flow by planning entry and exit framing so transitions match cleanly, a smoothness that develops through regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Uses close-ups and framing with intent. Advice to strengthen their impact by tying each close-up to a specific story beat, so the framing earns its place in the cut.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Maintains generally sound technical control. Advice to refine exposure and white balance by setting a reference at the start of each setup and matching to it, building consistency through regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Shows a clear understanding of visual storytelling. Advice to strengthen narrative clarity by making each shot choice serve one clear intent, a discipline that sharpens through regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'B', 'Overall work is competent and well-structured. Advice to refine both technical control and visual decisions through regular practice to reach a higher degree of polish.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Shows a basic understanding of exposure and colour. Advice to develop more consistent control by metering every setup and using a monitor or histogram to check, so even exposure becomes second nature with regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Applies lenses and depth of field at a basic level. Advice to practice with one lens at a time, observing how aperture and distance change the image, so focal choices become purposeful through regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Composition and camera angles show initial application. Advice to make clearer framing decisions using the rule of thirds, lead room and depth, building an expressive eye through regular practice.'),
  (1, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Maintains continuity in parts. Advice to strengthen flow by logging framing and screen direction for each shot and matching the next to it, a habit that grows through regular practice.'),
