  (4, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Coordinates camera and subject movement at a functional level. Advice to strengthen timing and clarity by rehearsing moves with the cast, so coordination improves through regular practice.'),
  (4, 'cinematography', 'C', 'Uses wireless focus systems at a basic level. Advice to improve accuracy through practice and anticipation — pre-mark focus points and rehearse pulls — building precision over repeated sessions. Regular practice will help build steadier control and consistency.'),
