  (6, 'cinematography', 'A', 'Demonstrates a clear, consistent visual approach, maintaining continuity in lighting, composition and tone. A confident command of visual identity. Good work.'),
  (6, 'cinematography', 'A', 'Makes informed cinematographic choices that support narrative intent and enhance audience engagement. A strong, story-led sensibility. Keep it up.'),
  (6, 'cinematography', 'A', 'Analyses cinematographers’ work with depth, connecting style, technique and storytelling impact. A mature analytical strength. Good work.'),
