  (1, 'sound_design', 'C', 'Currently student is at a basic level with Location Sound Recording. Advice to build this up: practise mic placement and monitor levels on headphones across more sessions to capture the clean, consistent location tracks professionals rely on. Regular practice will help build steadier control and consistency.'),
