  (1, 'sound_design', 'C', 'Currently student is at a basic level with Editing & Mixing Sound Elements using Sound Editing Software. Advice to build this up: practise regularly in the editing software and aim for cleaner, better-balanced mixes — this technical fluency is what gives a film narrative impact. Regular practice will help build steadier control and consistency.'),
  (1, 'sound_design', 'C', 'Currently student is at a basic level across the Semester I learning outcomes. Advice to practise outside class hours and repeat each exercise until it feels comfortable — steady, hands-on practice with feedback builds firm foundations. Regular practice will help build steadier control and consistency.'),
