  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Demonstrates strong control over continuity, progression, and emotional timing. Keep refining shot duration and emotional layering to push storytelling precision to the next level. Good work.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Shows confident shot arrangement and clear viewer guidance. To deepen emotional impact, keep exploring expressive pacing and reaction timing — let key beats land before cutting away. Keep it up.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Uses pauses and rhythm effectively to shape scenes. For an even more polished output, continue tightening continuity precision and transition smoothness across sequences. Good work.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Strong technical execution and clear narrative progression are evident. Keep developing more nuanced emotional shaping through deliberate shot selection and timing. Keep it up.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Demonstrates good understanding of expressive cutting beyond functional continuity. To strengthen dramatic emphasis, keep refining where and how long each beat holds. Good work.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Shot duration and progression are handled with maturity. Keep experimenting with emotional rhythm and viewer attention control to build an even more distinctive feel. Keep it up.'),
  (1, 'editing', 'A', 'Frames, inserts, and shot sizes are used purposefully. Sharpening timing precision further will enhance narrative flow and engagement. Good work.'),
