  (3, 'vfx', 'D', 'VFX implementation requires stronger technical understanding. To build this, work through the basic compositing and editing fundamentals step by step — layering, blend modes and clean cuts — rebuilding a simple shot until each stage feels controlled. This foundation strengthens through regular practice.'),
  (3, 'vfx', 'D', 'Effects appear disconnected from live-action footage. Focus on tracking, masking and scene integration — solve the camera accurately, cut clean mattes, and match each element''s lighting and perspective to the plate so it sits naturally in the shot. This integration develops through regular practice.'),
