  (6, 'vfx', 'A', 'An impressive pipeline with industry-standard finishing. As a final step, optimise render management for efficient high-resolution output, a discipline that matures through regular practice toward professional delivery.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'A', 'Advanced simulation work in particles, fluids and destruction executed with real conviction. Keep exploring physically accurate simulation methods to push realism even further, developed through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'A', 'Advanced simulation capability with realistic particles, fluids and destruction systems. To refine further, develop more physically accurate simulation methodologies, which mature through regular practice toward a professional standard.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'A', 'Professional cinematic polish throughout the film, showing strong readiness for industry-level production workflows. Keep refining your finishing craft to carry this standard confidently into professional work.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'A', 'Strong cinematic polish throughout the film, demonstrating readiness for professional production pipelines and practices. Continue consolidating these workflows to step confidently into industry-level VFX work.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Good overall integration supporting the grad film''s narrative. Advice to develop tighter consistency in lighting and shot continuity by matching tone and exposure across shots, which sharpens through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Strong compositing efforts on show. Advice to develop finer edge blending, closer colour matching and greater realism in CGI integration by matching to the plate — believable results come through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Effects enhance the storytelling effectively. Advice to develop greater subtlety and reduce visible compositing in complex shots through finer blending and detail work — invisible integration comes through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Decent camera tracking and stabilisation. Advice to develop greater accuracy in fast-motion and dynamic scenes by refining your track points and solve, which steadies through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Good environmental enhancement work. Advice to develop more depth, atmospheric effects and scene realism by layering haze and matching perspective, refined through regular practice and review.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'A solid post-production workflow. Advice to develop more consistent rendering and finishing polish across sequences by standardising settings and looks, which improves through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'Execution is effective, with occasional unevenness. Advice to develop uniform quality across all scenes by reviewing and matching shots against a reference standard — consistency comes through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'B', 'You have a working foundation to build on. Advice to keep developing advanced compositing and cinematic finishing techniques through regular practice to reach a professional standard.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Basic integration is present, which is a fair base. Advice to develop cinematic consistency and overall visual coherence by matching looks and finishing across shots — this polish comes through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Compositing quality currently varies across shots. Advice to strengthen the fundamentals of masking, layering and colour correction so results match consistently — this develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'CGI elements still read as separate at present. Advice to develop more believable integration by matching lighting, perspective and scale to the plate — realism here comes through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Tracking and stabilisation are an area to develop. Advice to practice reducing jitter and misalignment in key sequences by refining your track points and solve — steady results come through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Environmental effects are at an early stage. Advice to develop depth, shadows and atmospheric integration by layering haze and matching light to the scene — convincing environments come through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Rendering and finishing are an area to grow into. Advice to practice clean output with proper render settings so quality holds up to delivery — this discipline develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'Effects support the narrative in places, which is a fair start. Advice to develop a stronger planning and shot-breakdown workflow so effects are purposeful throughout — this approach matures through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'C', 'You are consolidating your core pipeline, which is the right focus now. Advice to keep practicing compositing, tracking, grading and continuity management — these skills strengthen steadily through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'VFX integration is weak and requires stronger foundational understanding of cinematic post-production. Build that base in compositing, grading and finishing — match elements to the plate and keep a clean, consistent finishing pass — so integration improves. This develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'CGI elements appear disconnected from live-action footage. Focus on basic compositing and scene matching — share the plate''s lighting, perspective and grain, and add contact shadows so CGI grounds in the shot. Integration develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Tracking and camera integration are inconsistent. Improve stabilisation and motion-alignment techniques — solve the camera carefully, steady the shot, and align elements to the camera move so they lock to the scene. Reliable results build through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Lighting and color mismatch significantly affect realism. Develop basic colour grading and correction — match exposure, white balance and contrast so each element shares the plate''s tone and exposure. Believable results come through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Masking and layering techniques need improvement. Practise clean, structured compositing workflows — tidy mattes, a sensible layer order and organised nodes — so composites stay controlled and easy to refine. This becomes second nature through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Rendering quality is below required standard. Focus on correct output settings and workflow discipline — lock the right resolution, codec and colour settings, and follow a consistent render checklist so shots deliver cleanly. This develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Visual effects do not consistently support storytelling. Plan and break down each shot before execution so every effect has a clear narrative purpose — decide what it does for the scene, then build it. This judgement develops through regular practice.'),
  (6, 'vfx', 'D', 'Strong emphasis needed on mastering core VFX fundamentals: compositing, tracking, lighting, and cinematic continuity. Work through each in turn — a clean composite, an accurate track, matched lighting, then consistent continuity — consolidating one before moving to the next. These basics build a strong professional foundation through regular practice.')
) AS v(semester, subject_code, grade, body)
JOIN public.subjects s ON s.code = v.subject_code
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
  SELECT 1 FROM public.comment_bank cb
  WHERE cb.semester = v.semester
    AND cb.subject_id = s.id
    AND cb.body = v.body
);
